name: FunnyAlphabet

”Alexa play funny alphabet”
”Alexa open funny alphabet”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny alphabet
des:
Funny Alphabet is an adventurous game that explores interesting themes like space, the ocean and pirates among others. 

As each stage is completed a medal is awarded.

It is packed with audio effects to keep things both educational and fun.

The game remembers where a player is up to, to ensure the content is always fresh and interesting.

To start say Alexa Play Funny Alphabet.
